    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Agirro Epicadi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> principi <expan><abbr>k</abbr><ex>astelli</ex></expan> Salthua <lb n="2"/>et Temeiae Glavi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan> fecit Epicadus <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>ut primum aetatis complerunt tempora vitae <lb n="4"/>et genitor fato conditus est tumulo <lb n="5"/>protinus inscripsit pietas nomen matrisque <expan><abbr>patrisq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>ut legerent cuncti genitoris nomina saepe <lb n="7"/>hoc decet ut nati componant ossa parentum <lb n="8"/>et cineri sedem substituat pietas
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): ILJug: Z. 5: patris(que).</p>
            </div>
